Package fi.tuni.work_time_tracker

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlterHoursFragment
    Fragment class to build tab Alter in application GUI and add Buttons onclickListener.
    AlterRowsActivity
    Activity class to Edit data at database and sets layout from activity_alter_rows.xml Extends from AppCompatActivity
    CustomListAdapterAlterRows
    Adapter for listing data from database to context in activity_alter_rows.
    CustomListAdapterDeleteRows
    Adapter for listing data from database to context in activity_delete_rows.
    DatabaseHandler
    DatabaseHandler class handles given data of object Workhour and saves, deletes or updates rows in SQLiteDatabase.
    DeleteRowsActivity
    Activity class to Delete data at database and sets layout from activity_delete_rows.xml Extends from AppCompatActivity
    HoursCalendarFragment
    Fragment class to build tab Hours in application GUI and add Calendar setOnDateChangeListener.
    InsertHoursFragment
    Fragment class to build tab Insert in application GUI.
    MainActivity
    Main Class for starting Application and using other classes for saving, deleting and editing workhours, Setting up Framgents to UI.
    SectionsPageAdapter
    Class for setuping fragmentlayout tabs for mainactivity.
    WorkHour
    Entity which is used to define and save data in database.
